description: Invest in the drivers of the blockchain transformation. The VanEck Crypto and Blockchain Innovators UCITS ETF backs the companies worldwide that are using blockchain to transform finance and other sectors. Valuations of publicly-listed blockchain companies have risen substantially in recent years, lifted by increasing users and revenues. As blockchain implementation progresses, these trends are likely to continue.
name: VanEck Crypto and Blockchain Innovators UCITS ETF
